      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: KYC Onboarding Framework for Neo-Vault Digital (High-Net-Worth Individuals)\n\nThis memo outlines the mandatory Know Your Customer (KYC) protocols required for the onboarding of high-net-worth individuals at Neo-Vault Digital to ensure strict adherence to anti-money laundering (AML) regulations. The process mandates rigorous identity verification, detailed beneficial ownership transparent reporting, and a dynamic risk assessment aligned with global financial standards. Compliance is enforced through automated anti-money laundering protocols that verify client data against sanctions lists and risk registries before access is granted. Failure to integrate these specific regulatory terminologies and procedures will result in immediate audit rejection by our automated compliance systems.\n\nApproved by: Compliance Office\nDate: October 26, 2023\nReference: NEO-KYC-2023-HNW",
      "source": "target",
